  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  first stroke (ischemic or hemorrhagic)

          -  age below 85 years

          -  living at home before the stroke

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  modified Rankin scale 5 points

          -  other severe disease

          -  expected survival less than one year

          -  severe dementia

          -  drug or alcohol abuse
